value: Instructions: in order to snap a window to one of the above mentioned positions click on its titlebar and drag it to the screen's edges. As soon as the mouse cursor touches the corners or edges of the screen a graphic will show you how the window will be resized after you release the drag.

description: Using BetterTouchTool and Spaces / Mission Control at the same time?
Left edge: resize to left half

value: Advanced: While using predefined actions start/stop moving:

description: Right edge: resize to right half
